blog.name: gweebs30
blog.title: Guy Murch - photographer
blog.description:
Love making portraits, fashion and creative photography. But will turn my hand to anything. My passion for photography began a few years back and I have spent that time shooting different styles to define the kind of shots that I enjoy creating.

Fashion and Portraiture is the route that I feel most fulfills the type of photography I enjoy and so this is the genre that I will be pursuing. I am always interested to hear from like minded people who would like to work together in creating Images that will add quality to our portfolios.

summary: JESINA CALCIO / DEBUTTO CASALINGO CONTRO IL SANTARCANGELO
title: JESINA CALCIO / DEBUTTO CASALINGO CONTRO IL SANTARCANGELO
body:
JESINA CALCIO / DEBUTTO CASALINGO CONTRO IL SANTARCANGELO

JESI, 22 settembre 2018 – La Jesina davanti al proprio pubblico contro il Santarcangelo.

tifosi della Jesina a Recanati

Dopo l’esordio a Recanati (1-1, reti di Magnanelli e Pera) i leoncelli debutteranno al Carotti contro l’undici romagnolo allenato da mister Galloppa che domenica scorsa in casa ha vinto contro la Savignanese (2-1 doppietta di Bondioli, Manuzzi).

Questo il tabellino completo…
